enumerations.name: DiagnosticTestResultUpdateEnum
enumerations.note: This meta-class represents the ability to define the update behavior of a DiagnosticTestResult. Aggregated by DiagnosticTestResult.updateKind

literals.name: always
literals.description:
Any DTR result reported by the monitor is used by the Dem.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: steady
literals.description:
The Dem accepts reported DTRs only when the configured debouncing mechanism is stable at the FAIL or PASS limit.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1
